      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a functional, budget-friendly option for those seeking reliable transportation. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scuffs, minor dings on the passenger side, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery exhibits significant wear and some staining, though all essential electronics and controls remain operational. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but potential buyers should expect upcoming maintenance items typical for a car of this age, such as brake pad replacement and a suspension tune-up. It is a solid workhorse that prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
